1. What user generated content SEO actually means in 2026
2. Why Google rewards UGC and which categories rank fastest
3. The 6 types of UGC, ranked by SEO impact
4. The schema, rel attributes, and crawlability rules that protect you
5. The 5-step moderation workflow we use for every client
6. Real ranking math, conversion data, and case examples
7. The risks, penalties, and recovery playbook if things go wrong</p>
